{"word":"G5391 - φιλόφρων - philóphrōn - fil-of'-rone - Courteous","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">φιλόφρων</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">philóphrōn</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">fil-of'-rone</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Courteous</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"சிநேகமுள்ள - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"friendly, kind"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5384 - φίλος - phílos - fee'-los/5384\">G5384</a> and <a href=\"#/G5424 - φρήν - phrḗn - frane/5424\">G5424</a>; <i>friendly of mind</i>, that is, <i>kind:</i> - courteous.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}